==== Nucléaire ====
{{Location map+|Chine|float=right|width=500|caption=Localisation des centrales nucléaires chinoises<br>
[[image:Red pog.svg|8px]]&nbsp;En service   
[[image:Green pog.svg|8px]]&nbsp;En construction
|places=
{{Location map~|Chine|label= Ling Ao |lat=22.60676045497342|long=114.5559722807801 |mark=Red pog.svg|position=left}}
{{Location map~|Chine|label=Daya Bay |lat=22.59888903084879|long=114.5486162853797 |position=right}}
{{Location map~|Chine|label=Qinshan |lat=30.43579429863514|long=120.9592802930963 |mark=Red pog.svg|position=right}}
{{Location map~|Chine|label=Tianwan |lat=34.7008928963106|long=119.4763380160776 |mark=Red pog.svg|position=right}}
{{Location map~|Chine|label=CEFR |lat=39.5|long=116.4 |position=left}}
